                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Porter</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Embassy of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-04-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 16, 1903</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Porter reports that war vessels of four nations went to Algiers and saluted
                    the President of France on his arrival there on April 15; that the President, in
                    returning from an important official visit to Tunis, will arrive at Marseille on
                    April 30. Ambassador suggests that United States war ships should go to
                    Marseille and salute the President on his arrival.)</p>
            </div>
